   Simple wave code which can have OpenACC directives added.


   ./clean.sh -->  removes files from data directory.

   ./run.sh -->    cleans up old files
                   compiles and runs pebble.f
 
                 generates files in the data directory
                 these files can be processed to make a movie
                 using GraphicsMagick
   cd ../mimage

   ./tpebA -->  runs a C program to convert the data/*.dat files into data/*.png files.

   cd ../OpenACC-Pebble

   ./runpmovie -->  runs a gm script to make a animation....

